Converse is now available for Apple Watch! With this update we now also turn your Apple Watch into a translation device. By leveraging the powerful new watchOS 4 you can now do real time translation right on your wrist. Use Converse on your Apple Watch. Fully optimized for watchOS 4. That means a faster smoother user experience. Flip the Apple Watch to show translations. Also new in iTranslate Converse: You can now also use the Converse iPhone App in Portrait Mode. The App now starts much faster. If you enjoy iTranslate Converse would you mind taking a moment to write a review on the App Store We d greatly appreciate it.
